<ref cRef="Prov." loc="28,3">Prov. 28,3</ref>; <lbl expand="translate">transl.</lbl>: <foreign xml:lang="gez">እምነ፡ አፉሁ፡ መዋግደ፡ እሳት፡ ወፅአ፡</foreign> <ref cRef="4 Esr." loc="13,11">4 Esr. 13,11</ref>; <ref cRef="4 Esr." loc="13,14">4 Esr. 13,14</ref>; <foreign xml:lang="gez">ሞገደ፡ ሥቃያት፡ ኀለፉ፡ ላዕሌሁ፡</foreign> Lud. ex Enc.; <foreign xml:lang="gez">ሞገደ፡ ጽልመት፡</foreign> Lud. e V.S.; <foreign xml:lang="gez">አዝማነ፡ ዓለም፡ መዋግደ፡ ኮነ፡</foreign> „tempora saeculi vicissitudinibus obnoxia sunt“ Lud. ex <ref cRef="Org." loc="3.">Org. 3.</ref> – <lbl expand="Vocabularium Aethiopicum, -a -a">Voc. Ae.</lbl>: <foreign xml:lang="gez">ሞገድ፡ ዘ፡ አዝዋሪ።</foreign> – Huc eodem referendum videtur <foreign xml:lang="gez">ሞገት፡</foreign> (quasi esset <foreign xml:lang="ar">مَوْجَةٌ</foreign>), quod legitur <ref cRef="Esth. apocr." loc="3">Esth. apocr. 3</ref>; <foreign xml:lang="gez">ኣስተናብር፡ ኵሎ፡ ዘሊተ፡ ይትኴነን፡ ዘእንበለ፡ ድንጋፄ፡ ከመ፡ ዘሞገት፡ ሠሪዕየ፡ ኵሎ፡</foreign> (<foreign xml:lang="grc">ἀκυμάντους</foreign>). {<ref target="#c1433"/> <foreign xml:lang="gez">ሞገት፡</foreign> passim occurrit ut <ref cRef="4 Esr." loc="9,16">4 Esr. 9,16</ref> in pluribus libris; <ref cRef="Sap." loc="14,3">Sap. 14,3</ref> in <lbl expand="d'Abbadie">Abb.</lbl> LV; item Plur. <foreign xml:lang="gez">ሞገታት፡</foreign> <ref cRef="Sap." loc="14,1">Sap. 14,1</ref> in <lbl expand="d'Abbadie">Abb.</lbl> LV.} </sense>
               
